OL,3,CThe Welsh boxer banned from competing
OL,4,Cfor British title because he was black
OL,6,FSimeon added: "I find it quite
OL,7,Fshocking that Cuthbert and his family
OL,8,Fhaven't received an apology."
OL,10,FMaking his directorial debut for this
OL,11,Fshow is Kev McCurdy, a fight
OL,12,Fchoreographer who has worked on
OL,13,FHollywood blockbusters and British
OL,14,Ftelevision classics like Doctor Who
OL,15,Fand Torchwood.
OL,17,FHe joined the production to shine a
OL,18,Flight on a chapter of black British
OL,19,Fhistory that he says was swept under
OL,20,Fthe carpet for too long.
