OL,3,CThe Welsh boxer banned from competing
OL,4,Cfor British title because he was black
OL,6,FHe said: "The play has got so many
OL,7,Fdifferent stories in it about the
OL,8,Fwarmth and passion of the character,
OL,9,Fthe injustice of what Cuthbert went
OL,10,Fthrough, from the time started going
OL,11,Fall the way up to the time he retired.
OL,12,FAs a professional he had 215 fights
OL,13,Fand won 151 of them.
OL,15,F"Back in the day it was very
OL,16,Fdifferent, but now if you want to go
OL,17,Fand do something, you go and do it.
OL,18,FFree of the injustice that goes on,
OL,19,Fand it still does go on."
